{"tid":325843,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)傲慢與屍變 頭條殺機 鐵甲威龍","createTime":"2017-07-17T13:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T20:01:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b900693eebdd4f6e6602e199523db5bd9a31fb","tid":325843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=OB4OchlGuQADUX0z5a5s3pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1dfc31cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK或者加V台個網入白名單好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=OB4OchlGuQADUX0z5a5s3pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8bc37c52\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=OB4OchlGuQADUX0z5a5s3pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e6f867cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/02/Pride_and_Prejudice_and_Zombies_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F02%2FPride_and_Prejudice_and_Zombies_Poster.jpg&h=15e3bcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d4/Nightcrawlerfilm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd4%2FNightcrawlerfilm.jpg&h=4a57db71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/50/Robocop_film.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F50%2FRobocop_film.jpg&h=ebe6a680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事設定於19世紀的英格蘭，敘述功夫一流的女主角伊莉莎白，一心想斬妖除魔，但因遇上高傲自負的達西先生而分心，兩人以往唇槍舌劍，現在卻是拳腳過招，不打不相識、不打不相愛。經過一番鬥嘴和好，兩人開始攜手對付殭屍，拯救小鎮....<br />\n<br />\n2.講述一名年輕的求職者Bloom在發現洛杉磯有一個秘密的自由媒體人團體，在夜晚拍下衝突、火災、謀殺和其他犯罪行為時，也加入到了從事報導洛杉磯地下犯罪活動的故事.....<br />\n<br />\n3.在近未來，持有各國政府國債的大企業，在各地政府破產後紛紛接管了各國政府機構，無政府資本主義成為主流意識型態，公司王國主導了的政府運作，OCP（Omni Consumer Products普及大眾商品）因而得到美國聯邦政府承包經營了底特律市政府，包括了治安的工作。<br />\n主角警員墨菲在一次剿匪行動中，被凶徒殺死後給OCP改造成所謂的機器戰警（Robocop），其實是一個有真人組織和電子機構組合的改造人，有刀槍不入的體格，充當了反罪惡的先鋒，可是墨菲後來人類意識回復，並知道自己本來身分的死亡，進而採取抓捕行動&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK啊啊啊"},{"pid":"6e767f36fe40e474d2c74ee1a2a342bf7cfd5103","tid":325843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446f828858e96bf85ed9115d917124ac62da79e8","tid":325843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ffb4042ff846efd8f65a4e081f165c374c4491","tid":325843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cd66431ccd5687b8d6f674f50da4c0a2b5fabc","tid":325843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:11:36.000Z","msg